## Use case
WidgetsApp's [backButtonDispatcher](https://api.flutter.dev/flutter/widgets/WidgetsApp/backButtonDispatcher.html) is recreated every time if the provided one [is null](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/blob/2.10.0/packages/flutter/lib/src/widgets/app.dart#L448).

Which is causing the following issues
- root / main `Router`'s dependencies [rebuild unnecessary](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/blob/2.10.0/packages/flutter/lib/src/widgets/router.dart#L751)
- nested `Router`'s `backButtonDispatcher` will lose priority since old parent is not wired anymore

Rebuild test outputs
1. initState _// state created_
2. didChangeDependencies _// state created_
3. didChangeDependencies _// Refresh MyApp button pressed or framework caused a rebuild_

